(2770, 1161, 'mfn-page-items-seo', '100+ pre-made layouts\n\nWe created awesome [tooltip hint="Click to scroll down"]100+ pre-made layouts[/tooltip].<br />Choose one of them and use for own business site.\n\nicon-lightbulb-line\n\ntop\n\n<a href="#thematic-websites">#thematic-websites</a>\n\nfadeInLeftLarge\n\nscroll\n\nFully customizable\n\nDon`t waste your time and within minutes create<br /> your website easily. You will love it!\n\nicon-beaker-line\n\ntop\n\n<a href="#">#</a>\n\nzoomIn\n\nFree support & updates\n\nThis theme is always updated on time.<br /> We also offer [tooltip hint="For support please visit theme forum"]free support[/tooltip] for all our themes!\n\nicon-comment-line\n\ntop\n\n<a href="http://forum.muffingroup.com/betheme">http://forum.muffingroup.com/betheme</a>\n\nfadeInRightLarge\n\nWhy you''ll love our theme?\n\nicon\n\n200\n\nshortcodes & items\n\nbounceIn\n\n100\n\n+\n\nlayouts\n\nbounceIn\n\n9518\n\nhappy clients\n\nbounceIn\n\n21\n\ndifferent pages\n\nbounceIn\n\nGuide for shortcodes\n\nicon-map\n\n<span class="big">See quick guide about some of included shortcodes and muffin builder items. We got over 200 in total.</span>\n\nicon\n\nzoomInLeftLarge\n\nShortcodes\n\n<span class="big">Building websites was never so powerful and easy! Over 200 included shortcodes and items gives you possibility to build <a href="#thematic-websites" class="scroll">any kind of website</a>. Choose between manual building and Drag&Drop Muffin Builder tool. You don`t need to be advanced user anymore.</span>\n\nMuffin Options\n\n<center><img src="http://themes.muffingroup.com/betheme/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/icon_muffin_options.png" alt="" /></center>\n\nzoomIn\n\nMuffin Builder\n\n<center><img src="http://themes.muffingroup.com/betheme/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/icon_muffin_builder.png" alt="" /></center>\n\nzoomIn\n\nhomepage\n\ndate\n\nDESC\n\nButtons\n\n<center>\n[button title="See all shortcodes" icon="icon-heart-fa" icon_position="left" link="http://themes.muffingroup.com/betheme/shortcodes/typography" color="theme"]  [button title="How Muffin Builder works?" icon="icon-layout" icon_position="left" link="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z7lRTlJVeT8" target="_blank"]\n</center>\n\n35\n\ndefault\n\ndefault\n\nStill not sure? See our <span id="thematic-websites" class="themecolor">latest demos</span>\n\n<span class="big">We have created 43 websites that perfectly fit to your type of business. Choose own and use within minutes.</span>\n\nicon\n\nzoomInLeftLarge\n\nhomepage-2\n\nWatch our video tutorial\n\nicon-play\n\nIf you prefer to learn from video tutorials, please click on the icon next to and watch video "How to re-create demo page" with step by step instructions. This is so easy!\n\n<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZACc1L9oXkI">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZACc1L9oXkI</a>\n\nprettyphoto\n\nzoomIn\n\nReady for e-commerce\n\n<span class="big">Create own online store and start earning money. Your customers will love design and usability.</span>\n\nicon\n\nzoomInLeftLarge\n\nicon-tag\n\nInstall WooCommerce\n\nDownload and install WooCommerce plugin. This tool is easy in use and got tons of configuration possibilities.\n\n3\n\nfadeInLeft\n\nicon-picture\n\nUpload products\n\nJust upload products with good looking images. Also setup options like shipping, costs and other stuff.\n\n3\n\nfadeInRight\n\ndefault\n\nicon-chart-line\n\nIncrease sales\n\nIncrease sales like never before. Lot`s of users got up to 200% because of nice design and usability.\n\n3\n\nfadeInLeft\n\nicon-users\n\nGet satisfied customers\n\nHappy client is good client. Customer who enjoy your shop will recommend it to his friends.\n\n3\n\nfadeInRight\n\nOur other awesome core features\n\nThat''s not all ...\n\nline\n\n[item icon="icon-tools" title="Best Muffin Options panel" link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n[item icon="icon-cog" title="Easy and fast Muffin Builder" link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n[item icon="icon-pencil" title="One click skin generator" link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n[item icon="icon-globe" title="WordPress Multilingual ready" link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n[item icon="icon-flag" title="Built-in Translator" link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n[item icon="icon-infinity" title="Unlimited layouts" link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n[item icon="icon-code" title="200+ builder items/shortcodes" link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n[item icon="icon-picture" title="Revolution Slider included" link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n[item icon="icon-palette" title="Unlimited colors" link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n[item icon="icon-docs" title="Outstanding documentation" link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n[item icon="icon-help" title="and much more..." link="#" animate="zoomIn"]\n\nButtons\n\n<center>\n[button title="Typography" icon="icon-heart-fa" icon_position="left" link="http://themes.muffingroup.com/betheme/shortcodes/typography" color="theme"][button title="Boxes & Infographics" icon="icon-layout" icon_position="left" link="http://themes.muffingroup.com/betheme/shortcodes/boxes-infographics"]\n</center>\n\n'),
